                        <h1>API CK-4, API FA-4 products: Mobil Delvac&trade; diesel engine oils</h1>
                        <p xmlns="">Mobil Delvac diesel engine oils help on- and off-highway fleets, fleet managers and owner-operators reach their business goals. Helping to increase oil drain intervals and boost uptime, these API CK-4, API FA-4 oils are designed to outperform current CJ-4 oils. Learn more about Mobil Delvac heavy-duty diesel engine oils below. If you can&rsquo;t find what you need here, please reach out to <u><a title="" target="" onclick="trackClick(this);" href="http://lubes.mobil.ca/Canada-English-LCW/where-to-buy.aspx" class="">authorized distributors</a></u>&nbsp;for more API CK-4, API FA-4 information.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <img src="../Canada-English-LCW/Images/440x200_why-pc11-is-better-caneng.jpg" height="200" width="440" alt="PC-11" title="PC-11" border="0" hspace="0"></p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <em>API CK-4, API FA-4 Mobil Delvac&trade; engine oils were compared to CJ-4 <br>
Mobil Delvac&trade; 1300 Super and Mobil Delvac&trade; Elite engine oils. The test results showed that the API CK-4, API FA-4 oils provided 20 percent improved wear protection,* 50 percent improved oxidation resistance&dagger; and 80 percent improved viscosity control.&dagger; In addition, the API CK-4, API FA-4 oils showed enhanced fuel economy potential (for FA-4 products only) and protection beyond original equipment manufacturer (OEM) oil drain intervals (ODI).<br>

                                <br>
*Based on a comparison of Cummins ISM and Mack T-12 engine test results.<br>
&dagger;Based on a comparison of Volvo T-13 engine test results.</em>
                        </p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <br>

                            <img style="height: 400px; width: 440px" src="../Canada-English-LCW/Images/4813-11_Exxon_Canada-English-chart_V5.png">&nbsp;<br>

                            <strong>
                                <br>
Mobil Delvac heavy-duty diesel engine oils</strong>
                        </p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <img src="../Canada-English-LCW/Images/150x150_caneng-bottles-advanced.jpg" height="150" width="150" alt="PC-11" title="PC-11" align="left" border="0" hspace="0" class="imgFloatLeft"></p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong>Mobil Delvac 1&trade;</strong>
                        </p>

                        <p xmlns="">Mobil Delvac 1 is an advanced synthetic diesel engine oil that provides extended drain capability and exceptional low-temperature performance with the potential to improve fuel economy.&Dagger; It meets or exceeds the requirements of OEMs, and its state-of-the-art technology provides:<br>
&nbsp;</p>

                        <ul xmlns="">
    
                            <li>Outstanding performance at extreme temperatures</li>
    
                            <li>Our best cold-weather protection</li>
    
                            <li>Our best protection for drivers with extended oil drain intervals</li>
    
                            <li>Enhanced emissions systems protection in a variety of severe conditions</li>

                        </ul>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <img src="../Canada-English-LCW/Images/150x150_caneng-bottles-premsyn.jpg" height="150" width="150" alt="PC-11" title="PC-11" align="left" border="0" hspace="0" class="imgFloatLeft"></p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong>Mobil Delvac&trade; Extreme</strong>
                        </p>

                        <p xmlns="">Mobil Delvac Extreme is a premium synthetic blend, high performance diesel engine oil that helps extend engine life while providing long drain capability for modern diesel engines operating in extreme conditions. Its boosted formulation provides:<br>
&nbsp;</p>

                        <ul xmlns="">
    
                            <li>Updated high-temperature performance/oxidation stability</li>
    
                            <li>Superior engine protection</li>
    
                            <li>Excellent anti-wear performance</li>
    
                            <li>Excellent soot and viscosity control</li>

                        </ul>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <img src="../Canada-English-LCW/Images/150x150_caneng-bottles-premcon.jpg" height="150" width="150" alt="PC-11" title="PC-11" align="left" border="0" hspace="0" class="imgFloatLeft"></p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong>Mobil Delvac&trade; 1300 Super</strong>
                        </p>

                        <p xmlns="">Mobil Delvac 1300 Super is an advanced diesel engine oil that meets or exceeds OEM requirements and delivers high performance in both on- and off-highway applications. Its carefully tailored formulation provides:</p>

                        <ul xmlns="">
    
                            <li>&nbsp;</li>

                        </ul>

                        <ul xmlns="">
    
                            <li>Performance for up to 50 percent beyond OEM recommended ODIs§</li>
    
                            <li>Outstanding high-temperature performance</li>
    
                            <li>Superior oxidation stability</li>
    
                            <li>Excellent soot and viscosity control</li>

                        </ul>

                        <p xmlns="">
