&dagger;Based on a comparison of Volvo T-13 engine test results.<br>
&Dagger;Compared to a 15W-40 conventional engine oil. Actual savings are dependent upon vehicle/engine type, outside temperature, driving conditions and your current engine oil viscosity.<br>
